 <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold-700">In this article</h2>
 <ol class="space-y-2 font-mono text-sm text-ash">
 <li><a href="#what-the-rule-requires" class="hover:text-gold-600">1. What the rule requires</a></li>
